{"tid":336840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[精神困擾]呢排情緒好似好有問題 好似有精神病","createTime":"2017-07-26T18:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T03:54:22.000Z","uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9463f89d625f729ccd9bd8c7ffd9c23439e66d","tid":336840,"uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:10:14.000Z","msg":"夜晚訓個陣 <br />\n一合埋眼就會FF自轟 同割脈 <br />\n如果唔係訓唔著<br />\n<br />\n個人又變到好躁<br />\nEg係火車到見到有人阻住我落車 我會好大聲咁喝鳩佢  完全唔覺得自己有問題<br />\n又會鬧鳩d朋友<br />\n依加係小小事都好撚嬲<br />\n打機又會好躁 以前好少會咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋開始唔想見人  尤其陌生人<br />\n依加連朋友都唔想搵 <br />\n但自己一個又覺得好孤獨<br />\n又好想搵人陪<br />\n唔想留係屋企 但又唔想出街<br />\n好撚矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係Fb IG 一見到d 朋友嘅post 就會好想留cm笑鳩佢地<br />\n開頭笑一兩個on9嘅都唔係咩問題<br />\n但進化到見到咩post 都有衝動去留cm閪鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪仲係正常<br />\n我覺得呢排好辛苦 心情同情緒都好差<br />\n定其實我只係週期性叫春<br />\n上黎問下意見先決定睇唔睇醫生"},{"pid":"a0ceba6546e789f9bb5bace28e3a9f46e8a5a29d","tid":336840,"uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69f724d4fce07a7e6119e01b5c069bf9f70e766","tid":336840,"uid":69791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"720cded3c5069f7f368f908956f1fb5d534ef481","tid":336840,"uid":31545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:24:19.000Z","msg":"得啦，唔好扮有精神病啦"},{"pid":"5420daaa275fc4de9991b88031cda296770d9362","tid":336840,"uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得啦，唔好扮有精神病啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好希望無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca55413b89671428b43e52660e26db445cb0d7fa","tid":336840,"uid":29203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:32:17.000Z","msg":"維持左幾耐？"},{"pid":"c124c18dc2cf9e500e4b3f94291